<% provide(:page_title, 'All Posts') %>
<% provide(:blog_active, 'active') %>

<%= render 'shared/navbar' %>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <div class="intro-lead-in">Welcome To The ITNT Blog!</div>
                <div class="intro-heading">Let's Start Hacking</div>
                <a href="#about" class="page-scroll btn btn-default btn-xl light">Tell Me More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">About</h2>
                    
                    <p align="left">ITNT Creative Designs is an all purpose design company with the goal of supplying our clients with all their creative needs. This blog is to support our efforts to stay current in the technology field, and support individuals who are interested in learning more about the industry.  Also, our blog post is here to help expand skills in various scripting languages, and give the knowledge to individuals to excel in this growing industry.
                    <br>
                    <br>  
                    It is our objective to be the best in our field, but it is equally important for us to share our creativity with the community and help innovate new ideas.  Through our own active research and hard work we look to give back on the things we have learned from others, and help create a standard that is both professional and high reaching.  By doing so we can play an important role in not just the work that we produce, but also the work that others are producing.  If there are specific subjects you wish to discuss, please don't hesitate to contact us and lets us know what you are interested in. 
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <br>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row text-center">
            <hr>
                <br>
                <h2 class="section-heading">Topics</h2>
                <br>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-code fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="service-heading">Scripting Languages</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">We discuss and supply detailed discriptions of various scripting languages, and what are some of the best practices when creating websites.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-laptop fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="service-heading">Responsive Design</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Responsive design is important today, and that is why we discuss the different ways to create a responsive design and how to implement it.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="service-heading">E-Commerce</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Looking to make money online?  We discuss how to create an e-commerce website, and how to create IPN and API's to take payments.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-cube fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="service-heading">3D Animation</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">We discuss how to create 3D Animations and how to apply different effects.  We also discuss the different ways to render animations and the best process.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-picture-o fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="service-heading">Graphic Design</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Graphics design is an important way to market any business. We discuss how to create different types of designs using Photoshop, Illustrator, and Indesign.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-microphone fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="service-heading">Audio Visual</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">We discuss the different ways to edit your video, how to splice up your video for a specified story line, and how to mix and master the audio for the best sound.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Portfolio Grid Section -->
    <section id="portfolio" class="bg-light-gray">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">Recent Post</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Check out the our blog.</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">

                <%= render @posts %>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

